Clone repository:

$ git clone https://www.github.com/randolf/simple-viewer-gl.git
$ cd simple-viewer-gl

Build under Linux and macOS:

$ make release
$ sudo make install

Optional copy executable in to /usr/bin:

$ cp sviewgl /usr/bin

Or symlink it:

$ ln -s sviewgl /usr/bin/sviewgl

Example of config in config.example file.
Copy it to $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/sviewgl/config
If $XDG_CONFIG_HOME is not set $HOME/.config/sviewgl/config will be used.
